Huora (noun)

A [[whore]] or [[harlot]], a [[prostitute]] (obscene).

More obscene if used meaning a female person who has lots of sexual activity with other people, regardless of their gender.

Even more obscene if you call a female person huora if they're not one.

REALLY obscene if you use it about a male person (as good as calling them a gay prostitute). Just don't do it.

Sometimes used more or less humorously to refer to a person who can be bought to do anything.

Finnish synonyms: [[portto]], [[ilotyttö]], [[prostituoitu]]